OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe magnitude of covering  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAlexei Navalny's funeral   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, We witness events, and we report on    
OL,6, them. But in the age of 24-hour news,  
OL,7, there is often precious little time for
OL,8, journalists to pause, take breath and  
OL,9, take in the magnitude of what has      
OL,10, happened.                              
OL,12,FIn the hours after Russia's full-scale 
OL,13,Finvasion of Ukraine on 24 February     
OL,14,F2022, I was filing non-stop for TV,    
OL,15,Fradio and the BBC news website.        
OL,17,FOnly at 2am the following morning,     
OL,18,Fafter my last TV live of the day, could
OL,19,FI stop and try to compute the enormity 
OL,20,Fof the moment. It has been the same    
OL,21,Fwith Alexei Navalny.                   
